Is that how you do things?

279
00:21:25,900 --> 00:21:28,030
You're gonna pay...

280
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:31,330
You'll pay!

281
00:21:35,830 --> 00:21:37,790
Don't get the wrong idea, brother.

282
00:21:37,870 --> 00:21:41,340
The reason I volunteered to go, the reason
I said I would be a human bomb,

283
00:21:41,630 --> 00:21:44,010
